aim_ag_texture_canyon

By BlackJack
-------------------------------------------
Small GunGame and/or Deathmatch 
map up to 32 players
-------------------------------------------
Took me about a week to finish this;
although it looks a bit squarish, it took
me alot of time to do all the damned
brushwork.

Plays nice with bots, good for quick 
encounters, and enough places to hide.
-------------------------------------------
CONTAINS A SECRET AREA WITH AWP!
HINT: You'll need to jump a bit.
-------------------------------------------
C&C are more than welcome.
